# Instagram Reels (Watch and Shop)

Add these variables to a `.env` file in the project root:

```env
VITE_INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_long_lived_access_token
VITE_INSTAGRAM_USER_ID=your_instagram_business_account_id
VITE_INSTAGRAM_PROFILE_URL=https://www.instagram.com/kabircollection6/
```

## Requirements

1. Instagram **Business** or **Creator** account
2. Account linked to a Facebook Page
3. Meta Developer app with **Instagram Graph API**
4. Long-lived access token with `instagram_basic` permission

## How to get credentials

1. Create an app at [developers.facebook.com](https://developers.facebook.com/)
2. Add Instagram Graph API product
3. Connect your Instagram Business account
4. Generate a long-lived user access token
5. Get your Instagram User ID via Graph API Explorer:
   `GET /me/accounts` then `GET /{page-id}?fields=instagram_business_account`

Without credentials, the component shows placeholder sample data.

## Product titles & prices

Map reel media IDs to shop products in `src/components/InstagramReels/reelsConfig.js` using `REEL_PRODUCT_MAP`.
